    "Sensor Data from Telecom Infrastructure.",
    "Sensor-based datasets are crucial for techniques like NumentaHTM and LSTM-AD, which focus on performance degradation.",
    "These datasets include measurements from network sensors monitoring variables such as equipment temperature, power consumption, and signal quality.",
